{"tid":1096132,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"3男女飛鵝山郊遊 一女子失足墮坡被困","createTime":"2019-04-07T13:43:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-07T21:57:21.000Z","uid":3090,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"ec2b453da46782577fc051baec4794cf78c132bb","tid":1096132,"uid":3090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T13:43:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JazjxBT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJazjxBT.png&h=d058268f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n救援人員將女子救回安全位置。司徒韋桐攝<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0hHpJJB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0hHpJJB.png&h=b6d4b9dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n女子不慎失足墮坡，一度受傷被困。司徒韋桐攝<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8yck1vo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8yck1vo.png&h=acb7dee2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n救援人員接報到場，正登山拯救。司徒韋桐攝<br />\n<br />\n2女1男今日相約到飛鵝山麥理浩徑第4段行山遠足，至晚上7時許，眾人途經標示M100近慈雲山觀音廟時，其中一名女子不慎失足墮至15米深的山坡，受傷被困，同行友人見狀報案。救援人員接報到場登山拯救，消防員游繩救起女事主，她手腳受傷，由救護車送院治理。"},{"pid":"4867bdb7006c8079a3caa0390085b43958171205","tid":1096132,"uid":164050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T13:57:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"000674a7a2827f32dfe3144cd7d84a8220952340","tid":1096132,"uid":188310,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T13:58:25.000Z","msg":"傻閪"},{"pid":"b173d6a025e1b7af147dea943842407870840a3c","tid":1096132,"uid":162511,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T13:59:20.000Z","msg":"傻閪港女肯定又自拍<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f08946841391a688704307e5040b5bbbf38b7224","tid":1096132,"uid":41093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T13:59:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好彩無事"},{"pid":"e67d00ea1647bb748fb84361229dd2f84f6fcd1a","tid":1096132,"uid":90946,"like":0,"dislike":0,